Sorta fitting we have a very unsettled atmosphere today=E2=80=A6and some =
thunder and lightning because the Natural Hazards lit up Jeffy last =
night with their thunder and lightning firing a spectacular 25 to vault =
them back in relevancy. The Mai Tai was flowing as she simply put her =
team on her back=E2=80=A6pony boy style and carried them around Jeffy =
like the proud warrior she is. I mean look at her scores=E2=80=A6a =
pretty solid 15 cap for 9 holes=E2=80=A6throws down a 43 on the =
night..literally beating ten other teams on her own ball. We always knew =
she had the ability=E2=80=A6just=E2=80=A6apparently=E2=80=A6way too many =
clubs in her bag! When asked about her amazing display and where she =
thought it came from she said, =E2=80=9Cwell, two things really..I had =
some good feelings today about my golf=E2=80=A6and a couple of Mai =
Tai=E2=80=99s before the round..but I think the real reason was the new =
sixth toe I had grafted in a few weeks ago on my left foot. I was never =
able to post up on my left at impact=E2=80=A6kept losing my balance and =
my coach thought this might help=E2=80=A6so I had it done. Yeah so =
it=E2=80=99s a camel toe..that they surgically attach to to the outside =
of my little toe..thus creating a more stable platform to move into on =
your downswing=E2=80=A6I snuggled a bit with the move last week in match =
play=E2=80=A6and didn't drink enough because Linda drank it all=E2=80=A6bu=
t it worked great tonight" I=E2=80=99d say so=E2=80=A6and there=E2=80=99s =
probably a lot of guys now looking for a camel toe.=20

Our leaders somehow fire the second best round of the night with a =
26=E2=80=A6even after the commish took down their caps=E2=80=A6how low =
can these monkeys go? They get Two T=E2=80=99s back from the industrial =
accident two weeks ago where the gang was using an air compressor to =
=E2=80=A6=E2=80=9Dfill up their butts=E2=80=9D and see which guy could =
blow the most up there=E2=80=A6well when Two T=E2=80=99s got past =
125PSI=E2=80=A6his small intestine blew=E2=80=A6thus landing him in the =
ER. The Good(?) news is he won the battle..and his prize was two tickets =
to see Air Supply at the casino in Royal City=E2=80=A6wow...lucky you =
dude. The CO continues his masterful manipulation of hiss =
handicap=E2=80=A6posting a nine on #1 when the pother three have him =
covered=E2=80=A6then a couple doubles..when things are still in =
doubt...then another 9=E2=80=A6a bogey and a par=E2=80=A6wait how the =
eff does one make 9 at #4=E2=80=A6and bogey at #5=E2=80=A6and then with =
no regret or care..he posts 11on #9 when their net birdie is locked up. =
I mean I do appreciate the 11..doing us a solid=E2=80=A6but the other =
huge questions is...if Bo is a 10=E2=80=A6who or what is an 11? Sydney =
Sweeney=E2=80=A6Megan Fox...Raquel Welch=E2=80=A6Farrah Fawcett. Mai Tai =
might argue for Robert Redford or Dr Dreamy...

ADL continues there string of good play firing 28 on the night and =
gaining a tie for 2nd place with 3 Jack. Capt Mauldy has been doing a =
great job of mixing up his troops=E2=80=A6keeping the commish off =
balance=E2=80=A6and last night it was that same Capt putting down his =
best round of the year going 5 under his cap with a short bag=E2=80=A6oh =
man there=E2=80=99s an easy wife joke there, but I=E2=80=99m not doing =
it because I actually like his wife very much=E2=80=A6him not so much. =
The ADL=E2=80=99ers  are looking very strong right now=E2=80=A6deep =
bench..the right mix of caps..and the experience of winning it all last =
year. There has been heavy money coming in on them recently=E2=80=A6and =
most of it has been leaving 3 Jack=E2=80=A6in fact since the day the =
commish took their caps down=E2=80=A63 Jack has seen about a 25% =
liquidation of funds...prompting the Pony to put a 5% cap on all future =
withdrawl's. Of course Special Ed has withdrawl's every day when drives =
by the Tractor Supply in Tukwila on his way to work=E2=80=A6seems theres =
a large statue of a a GOAT=E2=80=A6and Specials PTSD kicks in about that =
time=E2=80=A6somehow..someway they manage to hang around though and =
won=E2=80=99t be an easy out as they thrive typically in silly season.

Threeway!=E2=80=A6yep got a threeway going in T4 between Shots Shots =
Shots, What is a Foursome(adding the mailman to your threesome) and =
Stiff Shafts(which every threesome needs)=E2=80=A6which in terms of pure =
numbers would be technically an orgy? Or is 12 people engaged in sex =
just considered a nude beach? Inquiring minds wanna know=E2=80=A6 Shots =
fires 30 on the night and their season thus far is sorta microcosm of =
#3..where CB Buckner hits it to 3 1/2 feet=E2=80=A6but cant see the hole =
and thus misses. Yeah the par is good=E2=80=A6but we should have had a =
birdie and thats gotta change if they are gonna make a run=E2=80=A6no =
more shoulda, woulda, coulda=E2=80=99s=E2=80=A6time to step up and take =
what you want! The Foursome get the Wino and the Beaver back from their =
IL stints and the Wino goes 4 under his cap and should never play golf =
again with any more than 6-7 clubs in a bag. In fact his whole week off =
in rehab was not wine related but in fact mental imagery/management on =
how and when to hit certain clubs=E2=80=A6why a 56 vs a 60=E2=80=A6when =
to use a hybrid around the green=E2=80=A6how to hit a knockdown =
driver=E2=80=A6or a butter cut and most importantly=E2=80=A6how to hit =
the low fizzer!. Well the Wino is a good student and the lessons paid =
off. The Beaver on the other hand was out for two week for a different =
reason=E2=80=A6his father Ward was a iittle hard on him=E2=80=A6and he =
needed some =E2=80=9Cme time=E2=80=9D. Stiff Shafts are the sleeper team =
here in the top 6=E2=80=A6being the new kids on the block but ever since =
they got the T-Hawk signed to the new $324 million for 5 years contract =
a couple weeks ago it=E2=80=99s put a charge in them. They have been =
moving up a couple spots each week since and his tutelage of Mr Scott =
seems to be paying the most rewards as he shoots 5 under his cap last =
night leading them to 29.  Inexperience is about the only thing that =
might derail this group at this point=E2=80=A6that or a drunken sojourn =
into the depths of the seedy=E2=80=A6in which some hookers are bought =
and paid for by the Foursome=E2=80=A6and some inflammatory pics appear =
on the internet.=20

Joining the Hazards in 7th is DaddyShack who can only pull a =
threesome..not always bad=E2=80=A6but when it comes to golf..and team =
games..unless those three play well=E2=80=A6it=E2=80=99s a ride on the =
struggle bus and this struggle bus nearly broke down. They do manage a =
meager 2 under 34=E2=80=A6but =E2=80=A6we all know that sucks in this =
game pushing them down a few spots in the standings. The JV is back from =
a week off after tearing a Kegel muscle while on his honeymoon=E2=80=A6and=
 it clearly affected him. Shake and Blake was clearly at a disadvantage =
as the four clubs he brought with him were, a sandwich from jersey =
Mikes, a cudgel, a shillelagh and bludgeon to putt with=E2=80=A6and that =
produced the worst round of the season for him =E2=80=A6go figure.

Another threesome and nearly as inept were Shankapotamus=E2=80=A6enroute =
to 32=E2=80=A6pressing them backwards to 9th.BTO and the Engineer pick =
up a Honduran national who =E2=80=9Csupposedly=E2=80=9D can play golf =
when it=E2=80=99s  disclosed that JT and the DH we=E2=80=99re now  =
=E2=80=9Cholding out=E2=80=9D after playing so  well a week =
ago=E2=80=A6getting them back into contention=E2=80=A6their relationship =
became =E2=80=9Ccontentious=E2=80=9D..when it was disclosed that the =
T-Hawk got his $324Million deal. Well both JT and the DH want their =
bag=E2=80=A6and feel like mgmt is disrespecting them=E2=80=A6and they're =
probably not wrong=E2=80=A6but this mgmt mortgaged the future on Sam I =
Am a few years ago and still owes him 212$ Million=E2=80=A6not to =
mention we=E2=80=99ve only seen him once this year=E2=80=A6as reportedly =
he=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9Cjust not that into golf anymore" so there's no way =
these two are getting paid. ESPN is reporting that Palo Grande had some =
inquiries as to potential trade=E2=80=A6and we hear that Port O Putters =
had made a call or two as well=E2=80=A6and god knows they need them =
badly..

A shot behind in 10th at 258 is Beantown=E2=80=A6and honestly..we dont =
know if they are buyers or sellers right now. They Get Seve back from =
his IL stint where the BBL surgery he had required some =E2=80=9Camendment=
s=E2=80=9D and that took a couple extra weeks. Apparently when you have =
a butt let=E2=80=A6especially the Brazilian type=E2=80=A6those require =
inserts=E2=80=A6and if the inserts are the wrong size or dimensions as =
to what was spec=E2=80=99d=E2=80=A6you can have some issues. Well Seve =
