class=3D"">Sorta fitting we have a very unsettled atmosphere today=E2=80=A6=
and some thunder and lightning because the Natural Hazards lit up Jeffy =
last night with their thunder and lightning firing a spectacular 25 to =
vault them back in relevancy. The Mai Tai was flowing as she simply put =
her team on her back=E2=80=A6pony boy style and carried them around =
Jeffy like the proud warrior she is. I mean look at her scores=E2=80=A6a =
pretty solid 15 cap for 9 holes=E2=80=A6throws down a 43 on the =
night..literally beating ten other teams on her own ball. We always knew =
she had the ability=E2=80=A6just=E2=80=A6apparently=E2=80=A6way too many =
clubs in her bag! When asked about her amazing display and where she =
thought it came from she said, =E2=80=9Cwell, two things really..I had =
